Class OrgItem

  • java.lang.Object
    • de.tum.in.tumcampus.models.OrgItem

  • public class OrgItem
extends java.lang.Object
    An Element of the Organisation Tree. In the App a List of those Elements is showed (OrgItemList). The shown Elements are for Navigation to an Element without child-Element, whose details are then shown.
